            {
               "id": "navigation",
               "text": "<p><table class=\"book_navigation\"><tr><td><span class=\"htPrevText\"></span></td> <td> <span class=\"htTopText\"></span> </td> <td><span class=\"htNextText\"></span></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"index.html?page=class_content&arg=a86f373e-c908-4796-8a96-427ba5d4c889\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('class_content', 'html', 'a86f373e-c908-4796-8a96-427ba5d4c889', false); return false;\">Scientific method</a></td> <td><a href=\"index.html?page=sciense\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('science','html', '', false); return false;\"><span class=\"htIndexText\"></span></a></td><td><a href=\"index.html?page=class_content&arg=1acf8701-6c18-48c6-be69-196e3033538e\" onclick=\"htLoadPage('class_content', 'html', '1acf8701-6c18-48c6-be69-196e3033538e', false); return false;\">The writing system</a></td></tr></table></p>"
            },
            {
               "id": "group",
               "text": [
                  "<p><h3>Grouping</h3>In this chapter, we shift our focus to the natural world, exploring how natural phenomena have facilitated the grouping of matter since the universe's inception (<htcite0>). We then investigate the formation of essential life-sustaining structures (<htcite1>), and delve into distinct concepts applicable to living organisms (<htcite2>).</p>",
                  "<p>Concluding this chapter, we elucidate the methodology behind scientific method and address common misconceptions associated with it (<htcite3>).</p>"
               ],
